title: AAct 3.8.3 Portable [CracksNow]
description:
AAct - KMS-activator for operating systems Windows VL editions: Vista, 7, 8, 8.1, 10, Server 2008, 2008 R2, 2012, 2012 R2 and Office 2010, 2013, 2016. Also, you can activate Office 2010 VL on Windows XP. 

FEATURES - 
The program is written with use of original technologies and implements a different ideology design of such software tools, which is different from my usual practice. 

Program does NOT require any version .NET Framework. 

Whats New: 
- Added Save Settings. 
- Fixed bugs. 
- Added "/ip=" command line switches
